    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior presents well, though it does show minor signs of regular use such as small stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing only light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car is solid, with a complete service history that reflects its reliable performance. It\u2019s a dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality vehicle that has been cared for properly.",
