    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is looking for a new home and some dedicated TLC to get it back on the road. While it's currently in rough shape and being sold as-is, it represents a fantastic, budget-friendly opportunity for someone who loves a hands-on challenge. Grab this diamond in the rough and make it your next weekend project!",
