    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s as reliable as it is fun to drive? I'm parting with my well-loved car, and it's honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in solid shape, runs beautifully, and has plenty of life left for its next adventure. Whether you're commuting or heading out for a weekend getaway, this beauty won't let you down. Come take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust BMW E46 M3, powered by the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six delivering 333hp. This example features a 6-speed manual gearbox with precise synchronizer engagement and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical maintenance is up to date, including double-VANOS servicing and rod bearing replacement for long-term reliability. The chassis benefits from a reinforced rear subframe, mitigating a common platform weak point, and the suspension retains its factory-intended damping and rebound characteristics. Cosmetically, the car presents well with minor wear consistent with its age, but mechanically, it remains a sharp, high-performance machine ready for the tarmac.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean interior. Runs well. Reliable daily driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
