      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior paint still holds a brilliant luster, though a careful walk-around will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scuff on the passenger-side mirror housing\u2014honest wear for a car that has been enjoyed. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery is free of punctures or significant wear, and the carpets have been protected by all-weather mats since day one. All electronic components, including the heated seats, navigation system, and panoramic sunroof, are in full working order. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly with a steady idle, and the transmission provides crisp, seamless shifts. Recent service history includes a comprehensive multi-point inspection, a fresh oil filter, and a cooling system flush. The tires are high-quality all-seasons with substantial tread depth remaining, ensuring you're ready for the road ahead without immediate maintenance costs. This car has been a non-smoker vehicle and has been kept in a climate-controlled garage when not in use. It is a solid, dependable choice for anyone seeking a high-quality driving experience.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
